sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant UI as DemoHttpServer
    participant AC as AirCondition
    participant BC as SSE Broadcaster

    Note over UI, AC: User clicks "Turn ON" in the UI
    UI->>AC: Tell: PowerAirCondition(true)
    Note right of UI: Request returns immediately
    
    AC->>AC: Set poweredOn = true
    AC->>BC: Tell: AirConditionStateChanged(true)
    Note right of BC: Broadcaster sends SSE to all clients
